BodyName: Committee on State and Federal Legislation

Items.Title: State Legislation Resolution requesting the New York State Legislature to pass bills introduced by Senator Sanders (at request of the Mayor’s Office of Minority and Women-owned Business Enterprises), S.9351, and Committee on Rules (at request of Assembly Member Bichotte Hermelyn), A.10459, “AN ACT to amend the New York city charter, in relation to opportunities for businesses owned by women and minorities”.
Items.MatterName: Opportunities for businesses owned by women and minorities. (S.9351/A.10459)
